lead_paragraph: U.S. Democratic presidential candidate Hillary Clinton will meet with House of Representatives Democratic leader Nancy Pelosi on Tuesday in Washington, a Democratic source said.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton to Meet With Pelosi on Tuesday
